snippet.title: Flewn Trailer
snippet.description:
Flewn is the surrealistic story of an old whale walking on stilts through the desert in search of a lost ocean. More info at: www.FlewnStory.com
Flewn is out now! Download it here:  https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/flewn/id933350763?mt=8
